* {{ill|Tsushima Shrine|ja|津島神社|qq=draft|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Tsushima Shrine|qq=}} – Located in {{ill|Tsushima, Aichi|ja|津島市|qq=draft|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Tsushima, Aichi|qq=}}, the principal shrine of Tsushima Faith.

